{"text_id":164225,"tokens":["How"," to"," Prepare"," for"," IAS"," in"," India","\n\n","The"," Indian"," Administrative"," Service"," (","IAS",")"," is"," one"," of"," the"," most"," prestigious"," careers"," in"," India",","," attracting"," thousands"," of"," candidates"," every"," year","."," It"," requires"," a"," combination"," of"," intelligence",","," dedication",","," and"," hard"," work","."," Preparing"," for"," the"," IAS"," exam"," can"," be"," a"," daunting"," task",","," but"," with"," the"," right"," approach",","," you"," can"," succeed","."," Here"," are"," some"," tips"," to"," help"," you"," prepare"," for"," the"," IAS"," exam",":","\n\n","1","."," Become"," familiar"," with"," the"," syllabus"," for"," each"," exam",".","\n","The"," IAS"," exam"," consists"," of"," two"," stages"," -"," the"," Preliminary"," exam"," and"," the"," Mains"," exam","."," The"," syllabus"," for"," each"," paper"," is"," vast"," and"," covers"," a"," range"," of"," topics","."," Familiar","ize"," yourself"," with"," the"," syllabus"," to"," know"," what"," to"," expect"," in"," the"," exam",".","\n\n","2","."," Understand"," the"," competitive"," nature"," of"," the"," exam",".","\n","The"," IAS"," exam"," is"," highly"," competitive"," and"," requires"," a"," lot"," of"," preparation","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," understand"," the"," format"," of"," the"," exam"," and"," the"," level"," of"," competition"," you"," will"," face","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," develop"," the"," right"," mindset"," and"," approach"," to"," the"," exam",".","\n\n","3","."," Begin"," your"," test"," preparation"," early",".","\n","Start"," preparing"," for"," the"," exam"," as"," early"," as"," possible","."," This"," will"," give"," you"," enough"," time"," to"," cover"," the"," syllabus"," and"," revise","."," It"," is"," also"," important"," to"," maintain"," consistency"," in"," your"," preparation",".","\n\n","4","."," Choose"," an"," optional"," subject"," for"," which"