during"," the"," exam",".","\n\n","1","0","."," Take"," practice"," tests",".","\n","Taking"," practice"," tests"," will"," help"," you"," to"," identify"," your"," strengths"," and"," weaknesses","."," It"," will"," also"," give"," you"," an"," idea"," of"," the"," time"," required"," to"," answer"," each"," question",".","\n\n","1","1","."," Read"," the"," syllabus"," for"," each"," of"," the"," papers"," in"," the"," mains"," exam",".","\n","The"," Mains"," exam"," has"," nine"," papers",","," and"," it"," is"," essential"," to"," read"," the"," syllabus"," thoroughly"," to"," know"," what"," to"," expect"," in"," each"," paper",".","\n\n","1","2","."," Understand"," how"," the"," Mains"," differ"," from"," the"," Preliminary"," Exams",".","\n","The"," Mains"," exam"," is"," more"," descriptive"," and"," requires"," a"," deeper"," understanding"," of"," the"," subjects","."," It"," is"," important"," to"," prepare"," accordingly",".","\n\n","1","3","."," Go"," over"," papers"," and"," essays"," written"," by"," previous"," year","\u2019","s"," toppers",".","\n","Analyzing"," papers"," and"," essays"," written"," by"," previous"," year","\u2019","s"," toppers"," will"," give"," you"," an"," idea"," of"," their"," approach"," and"," style","."," This"," can"," help"," you"," to"," develop"," your"," own"," writing"," style",".","\n\n","1","4","."," Study"," current"," events"," and"," happenings"," in"," detail",".","\n","Current"," events"," are"," a"," critical"," part"," of"," the"," IAS"," exam","."," It"," is"," essential"," to"," study"," them"," in"," detail"," and"," understand"," their"," implications",".","\n\n","1","5","."," Practice"," writing"," answers"," to"," last"," year","'","s"," questions",".","\n","Practi","cing"," writing"," answers"," to"," last"," year","'","s"," questions"," will"," help"," you"," to"," understand"," the"," format"," and"," structure"," of"," the"," exam","."," It"," will"," also"," help"," you"," to"," develop"," time"," management"," skills",".","\n\n","1","6","."," Practice"," with"," a"," timer",".","\n","Taking"," practice"," tests"," with"," a"," timer"," will"," help"," you"," to"," manage"," your"," time"," effectively"," during"," the"," exam",".","\n\n","1","7","."," Ask"," family"," and"," friends"," to"," edit"," and"," review"," your"," responses",".","\n","Getting"," feedback"," from"," family"," and"," friends"," will"," help"," you"," to"," identify"," areas"," where"," you"," need"," to"," improve",".","\n\n","1","8","."," Review"," material"," in"," your"," optional"," subject"," in"," detail",".","\n","It"," is"," essential"," to"," review"," the"," material"," in"," your"," optional"," subject"," in"," detail"," to"," answer"," the"," questions"," confidently",".","\n\n","1","9","."," Practice"," with"," mock"," interviews",".","\n","Mock"," interviews"," will"," help"," you"," to"," prepare"," for"," the"," interview"," stage"," of"," the"," IAS"," exam",".","\n\n","2","0","."," Dress"," in"," a"," professional"," manner"," for"," your"," interview",".","\n","Dressing"," in"," a"," professional"," manner"," will"," help"," you"," make"," a"," good"," impression"," during"," the"," interview",".","\n\n","2","1","."," Make"," eye"," contact"," with"," the"," board"," member"," who"," is"," addressing"," you",".","\n","Making"," eye"," contact"," during"," the"," interview"," will"," show"," the"," board"," member"," that"," you"," are"," confident"," and"," respectful",".","\n\n","2","2","."," Be"," confident"," during"," your"," interview",".","\n","Confidence"," is"," essential"," during"," the"," interview","."," Speak"," clearly"," and"," answer"," questions"," honestly",".","\n\n","2","3","."," Answer"," questions"," honestly"," and"," directly",".","\n","Answer","ing"," questions"," honestly"," and"," directly"," will"," show"," the"," board"," member"," that"," you"," are"," sincere"," and"," knowledgeable",".","\n\n","Preparing"," for"," the"," IAS"," exam",